---
import '../index.css';
import { Sparkles, MessageCircle, Map, ChevronDown, ArrowRight, Check } from 'lucide-react';
---

<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Mes Packs Signature | L'orée</title>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-white text-dark font-sans selection:bg-primary/20">
		
		<!-- Navigation -->
		<nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full z-50 px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-zinc-100">
			<a href="/" class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-primary">L'orée</a>
			<a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold font-sans hover:text-primary transition-colors">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m15 18-6-6 6-6"/></svg>
				Retour au magazine
			</a>
		</nav>
		
		<!-- 1. Hero Section -->
		<section class="min-h-[80vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-6 py-20 bg-highlight/30 relative overflow-hidden">
			<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-20 pointer-events-none">
				<div class="absolute top-10 left-10 w-64 h-64 bg-primary/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
				<div class="absolute bottom-10 right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-accent/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative z-10 animate-fade-in">
				<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-serif font-bold text-dark mb-6 tracking-tight">
					Mes Packs Signature
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-poppins italic text-dark/70 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
					“Des offres douces, claires et lumineuses pour révéler ton univers.”
				</p>
				<a href="#packs" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-sans font-bold hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1">
					Découvrir les packs
					<ArrowRight size={20} />
				</a>
			</div>
			
			<div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce-slow text-primary">
				<ChevronDown size={32} />
			</div>
		</section>

		<div id="packs" class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 space-y-32">
			
			<!-- 2. Section Pack 1 — L’Éclat Express -->
			<section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
				<div class="order-2 md:order-1">
					<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-poppins italic mb-4">
						<Sparkles size={20} />
						<span>Pack 01</span>
					</div>
					<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-dark mb-4">L’Éclat Express</h2>
					<p class="text-lg font-poppins italic text-dark/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
						“La mini‑identité visuelle claire, rapide et lumineuse.”
					</p>
					
					<div class="bg-highlight p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-highlight/50 shadow-sm mb-8">
						<p class="font-sans text-dark/80 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
							L’Éclat Express est l’essentiel de ton identité visuelle, concentré en un format rapide, doux et professionnel. Une base solide, harmonieuse et cohérente, qui te permet d’être visible immédiatement.
						</p>
						<ul class="space-y-4 font-sans text-dark/80">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<Check size={18} class="text-primary mt-1 shrink-0" />
								<span>Palette de couleurs intuitive</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<Check size={18} class="text-primary mt-1 shrink-0" />
								<span>Duo typographique harmonisé</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<Check size={18} class="text-primary mt-1 shrink-0" />
								<span>Mini‑logo ou monogramme</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<Check size={18} class="text-primary mt-1 shrink-0" />
								<span>Moodboard directionnel</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<Check size={18} class="text-primary mt-1 shrink-0" />
								<span>Mini‑guide PDF (3 pages)</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					
					<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-8 mb-8">
						<div>
							<span class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40 mb-1">Tarif</span>
							<span class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold">250 €</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<button class="w-full md:w-auto bg-primary text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-sans font-bold hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1">
						Je veux mon Éclat Express
					</button>
				</div>
				<div class="order-1 md:order-2 relative">
					<div class="aspect-square rounded-full bg-highlight/50 absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-full h-full -z-10"></div>
					<img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/light/800/800" alt="Éclat Express" class="rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-2xl w-full h-full object-cover" referrerPolicy="no-referrer" />
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- 3. Section Pack 2 — La Voix Juste -->
			<section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
				<div class="relative">
					<div class="aspect-square rounded-full bg-accent/10 absolute -bottom-10 -left-10 w-full h-full -z-10"></div>
					<img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/voice/800/800" alt="La Voix Juste" class="rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-2xl w-full h-full object-cover" referrerPolicy="no-referrer" />
				</div>
				<div>
					<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-accent font-poppins italic mb-4">
						<MessageCircle size={20} />
						<span>Pack 02</span>
					</div>
					<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-dark mb-4">La Voix Juste</h2>
					<p class="text-lg font-poppins italic text-dark/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
						“Le message qui te ressemble, clair, aligné et émotionnel.”
					</p>
					
					<div class="bg-accent/10 p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-accent/20 shadow-sm mb-8">
						<p class="font-sans text-dark/80 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
							La Voix Juste clarifie ton message, ton positionnement et ton essence. Des mots qui te ressemblent, qui touchent, qui donnent envie de travailler avec toi.
						</p>
						<ul class="space-y-4 font-sans text-dark/80">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<Check size={18} class="text-accent mt-1 shrink-0" />
								<span>Phrase signature</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<Check size={18} class="text-accent mt-1 shrink-0" />
								<span>Pitch clair (2–3 phrases)</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<Check size={18} class="text-accent mt-1 shrink-0" />
								<span>Mini‑manifeste</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<Check size={18} class="text-accent mt-1 shrink-0" />
								<span>3 messages prêts à l’emploi</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					
					<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-8 mb-8">
						<div>
							<span class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40 mb-1">Tarif</span>
							<span class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold">220 €</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<button class="w-full md:w-auto bg-primary text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-sans font-bold hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1">
						Je veux trouver ma Voix Juste
					</button>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- 4. Section Pack 3 — Le Plan Lumineux -->
			<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
				<div class="text-center mb-16">
					<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-poppins italic mb-4">
						<Map size={20} />
						<span>Pack 03</span>
					</div>
					<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-dark mb-4">Le Plan Lumineux</h2>
					<p class="text-lg font-poppins italic text-dark/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
						“Une mini‑stratégie de communication douce, simple et actionnable.”
					</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="bg-primary/10 p-8 md:p-16 rounded-[3rem] border border-primary/20 shadow-sm">
					<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-12 pb-12 border-b border-primary/20">
						<div class="text-center md:text-left">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold mb-3">Visio 1h</h3>
							<p class="text-sm font-sans text-dark/60">Un moment d'échange privilégié pour poser tes intentions.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="text-center md:text-left">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold mb-3">Questionnaire introspectif</h3>
							<p class="text-sm font-sans text-dark/60">Pour creuser en profondeur ton univers et tes envies.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<div class="mb-12">
						<p class="font-sans text-dark/80 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
							Le Plan Lumineux remet de la clarté, de la douceur et de la direction dans ta communication. Tu repars avec un plan simple, cohérent, actionnable.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
						<ul class="space-y-4 font-sans text-dark/80">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<Check size={18} class="text-primary mt-1 shrink-0" />
								<span>Analyse éclair</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<Check size={18} class="text-primary mt-1 shrink-0" />
								<span>3 axes de communication</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<Check size={18} class="text-primary mt-1 shrink-0" />
								<span>3 formats de contenu</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
						<ul class="space-y-4 font-sans text-dark/80">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<Check size={18} class="text-primary mt-1 shrink-0" />
								<span>Mini‑calendrier 2 semaines</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<Check size={18} class="text-primary mt-1 shrink-0" />
								<span>PDF récapitulatif</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					
					<div class="mt-16 flex flex-col items-center">
						<div class="mb-8 text-center">
							<span class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40 mb-1">Tarif</span>
							<span class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold">150 €</span>
							<span class="block text-sm font-poppins italic text-dark/50 mt-1">(+30 € suivi 7 jours)</span>
						</div>
						<button class="w-full md:w-auto bg-primary text-white px-12 py-4 rounded-full font-sans font-bold hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1">
							Je veux mon Plan Lumineux
						</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

		</div>

		<!-- 5. Section FAQ -->
		<section class="bg-highlight/30 py-24 px-6">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-center mb-16">Questions Fréquentes</h2>
				
				<div class="space-y-12">
					<div class="group">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold mb-4 text-dark group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
							Comment se passe le paiement ?
						</h3>
						<p class="text-dark/70 font-sans leading-relaxed text-lg">
							Le règlement s'effectue en une fois à la commande pour les packs express, afin de garantir le créneau dans mon calendrier.
						</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="group">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold mb-4 text-dark group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
							Puis-je combiner plusieurs packs ?
						</h3>
						<p class="text-dark/70 font-sans leading-relaxed text-lg">
							Absolument. Il est souvent très pertinent de coupler l'Éclat Express avec la Voix Juste pour une cohérence totale. Contacte-moi pour un tarif groupé.
						</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="group">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold mb-4 text-dark group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
							Et si j'ai besoin de plus de pages pour mon guide ?
						</h3>
						<p class="text-dark/70 font-sans leading-relaxed text-lg">
							Ces packs sont conçus pour être minimalistes et efficaces. Si ton projet demande plus de profondeur, nous pourrons discuter d'un accompagnement sur mesure.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- 6. Section finale -->
		<section class="py-32 px-6 text-center bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
			<div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] -z-10"></div>
			
			<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				<p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-poppins italic text-dark/80 mb-12">
					“Prête à illuminer ton univers ?”
				</p>
				<button class="bg-primary text-white px-12 py-5 rounded-full font-sans font-bold text-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transform hover:-translate-y-1">
					Réserver un pack
				</button>
			</div>
		</section>

		<footer class="py-12 px-6 border-t border-zinc-100 text-center text-dark/40 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">
			&copy; 2026 L'orée — Design & Poésie
		</footer>

	</body>
</html>
